{
  "id": "1-1",
  "title": "Act 1: Daily Life on the Lower Decks",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch1_act1_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "titleCard",
          "args": {
            "text": "Chapter 1: An Unexpected Encounter"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Murky air mixed with machine oil and the stench of decay.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The lower decks of Terminal Ark were never a place fit for breathing.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "No one remembered how long the ventilation ducts had been clogged, and no one cared. A maze of exposed pipes ran along the walls, and the climate control systems wheezed along on insufficient power.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Dim lights cast their pallor on the wet floor, revealing not a trace of life.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "<em>{{characters.alea.name}}</em> stepped through a puddle and disappeared into the narrow corridor.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her pack contained half a block of compressed rations traded from the black market that morning, and an old canteen with barely half a tank of purified water remaining.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She hadn't received a job for thirteen days straight. Her food reserves had long since run out. This time out, she'd traded a set of freshly repaired work clothes for what little she now carried.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Eat, drink water, work yourself to exhaustion, then find a corner where you won't get kicked while you sleep—",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "This was the entirety of {{characters.alea.name}}'s existence on the lower decks for <em>eleven years</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "args": { "stay": true }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "subtitleCard",
          "args": { "text": "She closed her eyes." },
          "ms": 2500
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2700
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn"
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Numbers on the neural terminal status display glowed starkly in the darkness.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "display": {
            "topLeft": "Neural Terminal Status",
            "topRight": "● ONLINE",
            "bottomLeft": "Body Type ── Beta",
            "bottomRight": "Service Life ── <em>B15/9</em>"
          },
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "instant"
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Fifteen years and nine months.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "On Terminal Ark, the lifespan of a body was fixed—exactly sixteen years. Children used Alpha bodies; adults were transferred into Beta bodies.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "When the limit was reached, the body was reclaimed and the soul uploaded to the <em>National Archive</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "This rule had never been broken here—<delay ms=\"600\"/>except for {{characters.alea.name}}.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She had no memory of her origins, no recollection of anything earlier. She had awoken here on the lower decks, having never undergone a body transition ceremony.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her body seemed to have been born as Beta type, only with power output restricted during her youth—this was her best guess, but she had no way to verify it.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She passed through abandoned residential areas. A few children kicked an empty tin can by the roadside; hearing her footsteps, they looked up at her with blank stares before turning their attention away.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The people here were accustomed to strangers and disappearances alike. Someone sitting at the corner smoking cheap cigarettes yesterday might be gone without a trace today.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} stopped in front of a half-open iron door.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "This was her current shelter—the storage room of an abandoned clinic, barely large enough to fit a folding cot.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She opened her pack, placed the compressed rations on a broken desk by the cot, and lay down still clothed, closing her eyes.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Tomorrow's problems could wait for tomorrow.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2000
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "args": { "stay": true }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 750
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}
